t events and know the location of resources well enough. With your style of prose it would be a fascinating account. From it's beginnings at Hiroshima and Nagasaki, to the Cold War and absurd Hollywood movies. Sloppy work practises and disregard for safety in Russian reactor plants. Early mistakes in the US and Britain etc. How mistakes have lessened as we have come to a better understanding of nuclear power. How it's safety and environmental record actually compares to coal. A brief rundown on actual radiation from a reactor rocket program compared to radiation released from X ray diagnostics, coal burning, natural background levels and sunshine. <br>
